  "texts": [
    "Second, we randomly selected 30 questions to ask and evaluate using a computer method (code:random.choice(list,30)).",
    "The inclusion criteria were as follows: (1) questions related to brain rehabilitation; (2) answers by medical experts available; (3) publicly available question-and-answer pairs without involving personal privacy; and (4) no copyright restrictions.",
    "The exclusion criteria were as follows: (1) inadequate responses prompting further hospital visits; (2) questions focusing on severe complications in vital organs such as the heart or kidneys; (3) unanswered questions by doctors; and 4) questions violating medical ethics or Chinese laws in questions or answers.",
